   E-mail Updates from the Board

   Get on the list to receive instant updates by e-mail on Board
   activities and rulemakings.  Generally, updates cover activities
   related to the development of new or updated guidelines and
   standards.   (Past updates are posted in our news archives). Through
   these updates you will be notified instantly of new rules and notices
   as soon as they are published.

